# Secure Shell Daemon Hardening Configuration
PermitRootLogin no
PasswordAuthentication no
PubkeyAuthentication yes
ChallengeResponseAuthentication no
UsePAM yes
X11Forwarding no
MaxAuthTries 3
ClientAliveInterval 300
ClientAliveCountMax 2
AllowUsers secadmin

# Restrict remote access to your dedicated non-root admin user
AllowUsers <YOUR_ADMIN_USER>